(5000, 'Speakerphone SV13', 'public\\uploads\\sv 13.jpg', '<p>The SV13 is an innovative and professional speakerphone which can support USB,Bluetooth or 2.4G wireless at the same time.Powered by the EACOME innovative DSP technology, the SV13 create a realistic and natural experience conversation for your business requirement.Using the EACOME newest conferencing system, the SV13 is so powerful and easy to operate. Regardless of your location and timeline, you can enjoy the conversation anytime and anywhere.The SV13 is so stylish,smart and compact that it is ideal for open workspace, huddle rooms,home offices and travel.</p>\n<p>Feature highlights:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>&nbsp;Wide-band(48K sample rate) acoustic echo cancellation with HD-voice, dynamic noise suppression, automatic gain control, voice band equalization and intelligent microphone mixing</li>\n<li>Built-in multiple high-sensitivity microphones 360-degree pick-up,gather cover 5m</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Support USB,Bluetooth,line in/out and suitable for PC, video system,UC communication</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Support 2.4G wireless transmission, no need any cable connection</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Cascading: support up to 3pcs SV13 cascading,available for more attendees and larger meeting room</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Multi-party collaboration: bridge mobile call,USB VoIP call and video call together conveniently</li>\n<li>Speaker volume up to 86dB, 16 levels adjustable</li>\n<li>Available to plug any headset to make private conversation in open environment</li>\n<li>The gorgeous and clear LED is very helpful to know all working status and operation</li>\n</ul>', NULL, 118, 7),
(5001, 'Multi-Party Conference PhoneS350PB', 'public\\uploads\\s350.png', '<p>Income HD conference phone S350PB (EACOME S350PB) series is a Bluetooth conference phone and an ordinary telephone line conference phone. It adopts the international advanced SonicClear IV high-definition voice processing technology. It can be connected to ordinary telephone lines for conference calls, and can also be connected to Bluetooth communication devices such as mobile phones or computers. It is easy to implement mobile phone hands-free conference calls or network conferences. More importantly, it has a built-in conference bridge function, which can mix the above two conferences. Thereby, a three-party audio conference is held, and the video conference and the audio conference are bridged together to communicate with each other. The call quality is stable and reliable, the sound quality is clear and natural, and the experience is comfortable and pleasant!</p>\r\n<p>S350PB does not require signal connection lines (such as USB cable, analog audio cable) to connect, and transmits signals to docking communication devices through Bluetooth, which greatly simplifies and beautifully arranges the wiring and connection of conference rooms, and realizes video and network conferences quickly and efficiently.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;S350PB has one machine and multiple uses, avoiding the purchase of multiple conference phones; simplifying the complex communication system of video and audio, and simplifying the layout of the conference room. It is undoubtedly a multi-purpose and multi-functional conference phone terminal Conference system with powerful and efficient collaborative office capabilities.</p>\r\n<p>The S350PB has four high-performance microphones and two optional expansion microphones. It has six completely independent voice processing channels. Therefore, the microphone can collect sound at distances of up to 5 meters and has high-definition voice quality. Very suitable for medium and large conference rooms, important conference rooms and important meetings.</p>\r\n<p><br />The S350PB has four high-performance microphones and two optional expansion microphones. It has six completely independent voice processing channels. Therefore, the microphone can collect sound at distances of up to 5 meters and has high-definition voice quality. Very suitable for medium and large conference rooms, important conference rooms and important meetings.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>S350PB conference phone has powerful and practical functions.</li>\r\n<li>Suitable for meeting rooms of 20-60 square meters, supporting on-site meetings of up to 15 people. Built-in 4 microphones, microphone collection distance of 3 meters, covering the full range of 360 degrees.</li>\r\n<li>Supports two external microphone input, the pickup radius reaches 5 meters.</li>\r\n<li>Support analog PBX, PSTN and other common analog telephone communication networks.</li>\r\n<li>Support Bluetooth wireless transmission function, no need to connect cable to video terminal, PC and other communication equipment</li>\r\n', NULL, 118, 7),
(5002, 'Speakerphone S210', 'public\\uploads\\s210.png', '<p>Eacome conference microphone/speakerphone S210 series is automatically adapting in 48KHz fullduplex echo cancellation. It\'s contributing in conference calls that sound as natural as being there. Any time there will be no noise at both sites or multi-parties. S210 creates a more realistic and joyful experience in conference phone calls for users.</p>\n<p>The high quality audio sound and 360-degree microphone enables everyone to hear and be heard from all angles across the speakerphone. But that\'s not all &ndash; you can also use Eacome S210 for listening to your favorite multimedia with crystal clear clarity.</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Features:</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>&nbsp;Set up a conference call in seconds</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Conference calls via Bluetooth/2.4G wireless and USB connection</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Great sound for calls and streaming multimedia</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Connect to your PC, tablet, or smart phone</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Easy to use with dedicated answer/end, volume control, and mute buttons</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Plug and play</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>HD Voice for conversations in high definition sound quality</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Compatible with Windows Microsoft Lync and Microsoft Office Communicator</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Compact and portable design</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Built-in chargeble battery: talk time 3 hours</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</li>\n</ul>', NULL, 118, 7),
(5003, 'Speakerphone SV11', 'public\\uploads\\sv11.jpg', '<p>Speaker phone for individual, small group use. The SV11 connect to PCs for rich, full-duplex audio communications and can be used with VoIP softphones, Web collaboration, instant messaging and any other applications requiring two-way audio via USB. A perfect addition to the offifice or conference room for greatly enhanced collaboration.</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Feature Highlights:</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Echo Cancellation,Noise Suppression and Automatic gain control.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Microphone coverage: 3 meters, 360 degree range</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Exquisite and small,it\'s convenient to carry.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Conference calls via USB connection.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Support all kinds of Web Conferencing:IBM Workplace,Microsoft Live Meeting,WebEx,etc.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Support all kinds of VoIP Softphones:Avaya, Cisco, Nortel, Mirial,etc.Support all kinds of Internet Telephony:Google Talk, Skype, Lync,Vonage,etc.Support all kinds of Instant Messenger:QQ, AOL, MSN, Yahoo,etc.Support earphone mode and could hold a private communication with it.Speaker volume up to 80dB.Support a variety of system:WinXP,Win7/Win8/Win10,Mac OSX,Android .</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</li>\n</ul>', NULL, 118, 7),
(5004, 'Video Collaboration System SV3100', 'public\\uploads\\sv3100.png', '<p>The SV3100, our video conferencing solution for small to medium-sized meeting rooms, delivers high quality HD video and crystal clear audio, allowing any meeting place to be a video collaboration space. With advanced features like acoustic echo cancellation, noise reduction technology, and intuitive controls, it\'s easier than ever to includeeveryone in the conversation. The SV3100 is so stylish, smart and amazing that is ideal for your meeting.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 119, 7),
(5005, 'Video Collaboration System SV3600', 'public\\uploads\\sv3100.png', '', NULL, 119, 7),
(5006, 'VoIp Series IP6000', 'public\\uploads\\IP6000.jpg', '<p>Eacome VoIP conference phone IP600 is equipped with the international advanced SonicClear IV HD-voice processing technology. This model is designed for SIP VoIP and USB environments, with unique features that take advantage of the benefits provided by the different types of telephony environments. You can combine and switch easily between among these connectivity to make a multi-party conference call with kinds of telephony platform. With highly stable and reliable acoustic performance, these products create a more realistic and joyful experience in conference phone calls for users.With the conference phone dedicated so many connectivity, you can easily hold a 3-way SIP conference call in IP network, make a conference call between video conferencing system via USB connection with IP PBX system. It can replace multiple conference phones and simplify the conference room layout. It is undoubtedly a broader telephony platform for remote collaboration.</p>\n<p>IP600 is equipped with four internal uni-directional microphones and two external microphones, it\'s resulting in microphones that can gather cover 5 meters with more high-definition voice quality. They offer an auxiliary audio port to connect to external speaker devices so that it will enlarge the speaker coverage range. Therefore, these products are suitable for different types of environment such as larger conference rooms, medium meeting rooms.</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Feature Highlights:</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Wide-band acoustic echo cancellation with NS,AGC and intelligent microphone mixing.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Best for conference room within 20-60m\' and supports audio teleconferencing within 15 attendees.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>&nbsp;4 inner uni-directional microphones gather over 3m, 360 degree range.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Support two extension microphones gather over 5 meters.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Support VoIP communication network, SIP2.0 protocol.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>&nbsp;Support 3 independent SIP accounts.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Built-in 4-way VoIP multi-party conference call, support USB connectivity and multi-party conference call.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>&nbsp;Support USB, designed for video conferencing system, web conference, UC unified communication platform, VPN platform etc.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Collaboration: integrated VoIP network, USB VoIP multi-party conference call, can expand video conferencing or web conferencing to an IP conference call.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Support audio output to the amplifier and mixing consoles, expand the room-coverage options to meet the requirements of larger meeting rooms.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Speaker volume up to 95db,16 levels adjustable.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>128\'64 full dot matrix graphic LCD display with ivory white backlight.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Multiple languages display, support Chinese and English.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Built-in Web GUI for configuration and provisioning.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Powerful phonebook function: store 140 entries including ', NULL, 120, 7),
(5007, 'Echo Cancellation T220', 'public\\uploads\\T220.jpg', '<p>T220 is an industry-leading, professional echo canceller with high performance DSP processing and stable operation. Powered by the improved SonicClear III HD voice processing technology, it is contributing the widest band full-duplex acoustic echo cancellation of 20Hz-16KHz covering the human hearing range. T220 echo canceller can be used for audio teleconferencing and video conferencing to maintain both local and remote meeting smoothly.</p>', NULL, 121, 7),
(5008, 'Echo Cancellation T440', 'public\\uploads\\T440.jpg', '<p>Eacome sound reinforcement T440 series supports PSTN ,VoIP and USB VoIP networks, which provides a holistic high quality solution for traditional PBX network,VoIP network and video conferencing system. Users can make converged unied communication by connecting to telephone line, computer and high denition videoconferencing system directly to hold an interactive immersive audio</p>', NULL, 121, 7),
