(5042, 'WanderCam 25w', 'public\\uploads\\DC-2.png', '<p>The QOMO WanderCam 25w is a low budget wireless document camera you can count on. Share and save high resolution photos and videos instantly from anywhere in the classroom.</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Product Specifications</strong></span></p>\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Wireless Connection&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">: 2.5GHz Wi-Fi, USB dongle</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Sensor&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">: CMOS</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Camera Rotation&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">: 270 degrees</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Digital Zoom&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">: 16x</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Video Resolution&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">: 720p, 1080p</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Image Resolution</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">: 5MP</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">File Format&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">: JPG, BMP, PNG, GIF, and TIF for pictures; PDF, DOC, TXT, RTF, XLS for files; FLV, MP4, AVI for video</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Shooting Area&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">: A4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Frame Rate&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">: 30 fps</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Wi-Fi Range&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">:150 feet</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Software&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">: QOMO QView Wireless (included)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Operating Systems&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">: Windows, Mac,Android (software features may differ across platforms)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Operating Dimensions&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">: 13 in x 2.5 in x 1.75 in (folded), 1