(5184, 'X Fixed', 'public\\uploads\\Flex  glass.png', '<p>Stop buying rigid panel, glass rear-projection screens! With FlexGlass, you can configure your screen into many different shapes such as an S-Shape or even a 360&deg; circle due to its flexible nature. Even with all that flexibility, FlexGlass still maintains that look we all know and love from standard glass rear-projection systems. It really is the best of both worlds.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Max Width&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">1212&Prime;<br />(30785mm)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Max Viewing Height&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">103&Prime;<br />(2616mm)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Resolution&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">4k</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Gain&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">.6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Half Gain&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">75&deg;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Minimum Throw&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">0.2 x Image Width</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Projection Type&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Rear Only</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">Opaque&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\">No</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1012, 108, 3),
(5185, 'Black Diamond Film', 'public\\uploads\\bd-film-application.jpg', '<p>Black Diamond Film encompasses a permanent pressure sensitive adhesive and release liner for easy application. Simply put, Black Diamond Film is applied like window tint, making installation very easy and pain free.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><strong>Black Diamond Film .8</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><strong>Black Diamond Film 1.4</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">Max Width</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">1176&Prime;<br />(29870mm)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">1176&Prime;<br />(29870mm)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">Max Viewing Height &nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">60&Prime;<br />(1524mm)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">60&Prime;<br />(1524mm)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">Resolution</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">8k</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">8k</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">Gain&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">.8&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">1.4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">ALR&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">65%&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">55%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">Half Gain&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">37&deg;&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">41&deg;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">Minimum Throw</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">1.2 x Image Width</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">1.2 x Image Width</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">Projection Type</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">Rear Only</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">Rear Only</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">Opaque&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">No</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\">No</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', 1012, 108, 3),
